  <brief_title>Evaluation of Deep Transcranial Magnetic Stimulation (TMS) H-Coil in the Treatment of Major Depression</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the H1 Coil and H2 Coil TMS Device - Safety and Feasibility in Major Depression Episode</official_title>
